    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Begonia akaw. A. Habit; B. Stipule; C. Bract; D. Inflorescence; E. Androecium; F. Pistillate flower lateral view; G. Ovary cross section. Illustrated by J. Mansibang based on AAMNP173 (PNH, BRIT, CAHUP)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8297091/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8297093>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Begonia akaw. A. Habitat and habit; B. Stem; C. Stipule; D. Leaf adaxial (left) and abaxial (right) surface; E. Inflorescence showing bracts; F. Inflorescence showing peduncle; G. Staminate flower ventral view; H. Staminate flower ventral view, a variant with rounder tepals; I. Staminate flower lateral view; J. Pistillate flower ventral view; K. Pistillate flower lateral view showing ovary; L. Ovary cross section; M. capsule. All photos by Y.P. Ang." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8297093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

